cascading.tuple.io

Class TuplePair

  • java.lang.Object
    • cascading.tuple.Tuple
      • cascading.tuple.io.TuplePair
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Object>, Iterable<Object>

    public class TuplePair
extends Tuple
    Class TuplePair is a utility class that is optimized to hold two Tuple instances for sorting and hashing of each part independently.
